SIX people are reported to have died in yet another mass shooting KwaZulu-Natal. This recent tragedy happened in Marianhill where is it reported that three armed men and opened fire at people who were a tuck shop. It is not clear if the shooting link to the recent shooting that happened in the province of KZN or the one in Orlando East in Gauteng. The motive of the shooting is also unknown at this stage. READ: MDLALOSE SHOOTING: ‘We know who suspects are’ Over the past few weeks, going to taverns has become a suicide mission. Tavern owners previously told Daily Sun that they fear that the recent spate of shootings may impact their businesses, which are their bread and butter, negatively.